---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../../components/Card.astro';
---

<Layout title="Music & Piano | Aarya Patel">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 space-y-6">

    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section class="text-center py-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">🎹 Music & Piano</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">My musical journey</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Piano Journey -->
    <Card title="My Piano Journey" emoji="🎹">
      <p class="mb-4">I love playing the piano! Music is one of my favorite hobbies alongside coding and math.</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        Playing piano helps me relax and express myself creatively. It also teaches me discipline and patience -
        just like coding, you have to practice regularly to get better!
      </p>
    </Card>

    <!-- Coming Soon -->
    <Card title="More Coming Soon!" emoji="🎵">
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        I'm still building this section! Check back later for updates about my musical progress,
        favorite pieces, and more.
      </p>
    </Card>

    <!-- Connection to Coding -->
    <Card title="Music & Coding" emoji="🔗">
      <p class="mb-4">Did you know music and coding have a lot in common?</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
        <li>Both require pattern recognition and logical thinking</li>
        <li>Music has algorithms (scales, chord progressions)</li>
        <li>Coding can create music (digital audio, music software)</li>
        <li>Both need regular practice to master</li>
      </ul>
    </Card>

    <!-- Back to Home -->
    <div class="text-center pt-4">
      <a href="/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">← Back to Home</a>
    </div>

  </div>
</Layout>
